biography.bio: Timo Kahilainen was born in 1963 as Timo Eero Kahilainen. He is an actor and writer, known for Kummeli Alivuokralainen (2008), Kummeli Goldrush (1997) and Kummeli Stories (1995).
biography.name: Timo Kahilainen

biography.bio: Heikki Vihinen was born in 1964 in Tampere, Finland. He is an actor and writer, known for Kummeli Goldrush (1997), Kummelin Jackpot (2006) and Kummeli Alivuokralainen (2008).

biography.bio: Heikki Hela was born in 1964. He is an actor and writer, known for Kummeli Goldrush (1997), Kummeli Stories (1995) and Handcuff King (2002). He has been married to Mari Posti since 1996. They have two children.
biography.name: Heikki Hela

biography.bio: Heikki Silvennoinen was born on April 27, 1954 in Savonlinna, Finland as Heikki Johannes Silvennoinen. He is an actor and writer, known for Kummeli Goldrush (1997), Kummeli Stories (1995) and Kummelin Jackpot (2006). He has been married to Tiina Lähteenmäki since August 1998.
biography.name: Heikki Silvennoinen

biography.bio: Kaisa Hela was born in 1977 in Jyväskylä, Finland. She is an actress and writer, known for The Good Son (2011), Beauty and the Bastard (2005) and Kummeli V (2014).
biography.name: Kaisa Hela

biography.bio: Tom Pöysti was born on May 14, 1954 in Helsinki, Finland as Tom Erik Pöysti. He is an actor, known for Jäitä hattuun (1994), A Charming Mass Suicide (2000) and Mannen utan ansikte (1995).
biography.name: Tom Pöysti

biography.bio: Ville Myllyrinne was born on July 14, 1973 in Vantaa, Finland as Ville Tapani Myllyrinne. He is an actor and writer, known for Ketonen & Myllyrinne (2006), Koistiset lennossa (2012) and Miss Zahra (2015). He is married to Anu Hakkarainen. They have one child.
biography.name: Ville Myllyrinne

biography.bio: Jussi Vatanen is an actor and writer, known for Presidentin kanslia (2008), Very Cold Trip (2010) and Lapland Odyssey 2 (2015).
biography.name: Jussi Vatanen

biography.bio: Actor /Screenwriter Kari Hietalahti is best known for having appeared in several popular Finnish television series, such as Vintiöt, Ihmisten puolue, Ihmebantu, Pasila, Kimmo and Roba, and in films such as Hellsinki, Vares- Private eye and Boy Upside Down. In August 2011, Hietalahti's first book "Kenraali Pancho & Pojat - Suuri kalottikirja" was published. Hietalahti likes flyfishing and he is an Ambassador of the Vision Fly Fishing.
biography.name: Kari Hietalahti

biography.bio: Markku Toikka was born on April 5, 1955 in Somero, Finland. He is an actor, known for Crime et châtiment (1983), Puhtaat valkeat lakanat (1993) and Upswing (2003).
biography.name: Markku Toikka

biography.bio: Iina Kuustonen was born in 1984. She is an actress and writer, known for Summertime (2014), Sanaton sopimus (2007) and Adult Camp (2015).
biography.name: Iina Kuustonen

biography.bio: Kaarina Hazard is an actress and writer, known for Lettres au Père Jacob (2009), Hopeanuolet (2007) and Hardly a Butterfly (1998).
biography.name: Kaarina Hazard

biography.bio: Seela Sella was born on December 30, 1936 in Tampere, Finland as Seela Maini Marjatta Virtanen. She is an actress, known for The Leaning Tower (2006), The Last Medals (2000) and Sylvin kamari (2000). She was previously married to Elis Sella.
biography.name: Seela Sella

biography.bio: Ilkka Heiskanen was born on January 11, 1962 in Hamina, Finland. He is an actor and writer, known for Beyond Enemy Lines (2004), The Mercenary Soldier (1997) and Silence (2011).
biography.name: Ilkka Heiskanen

biography.bio: Riku Suokas was born on December 29, 1971 in Tampere, Finland as Riku Tapani Suokas. He is an actor and director, known for Vuonna 85 (2013), Kuka uskoo haikaraa? (1984) and Kummeli V (2014). He has been married to Katariina Kuisma since 1994.
biography.name: Riku Suokas
